title: Wheat Crop Acreage for Germany
notes:
Series Is Presented As Three Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1878-1917 (2)--Original Data, 1911-1937 (3)--Original Data, 1933-1944. Boundaries Exclude All Ceded Territory. Data For 1936-1937 Were Computed By Deducting The Average For The Saarland (See Statistiches Jahrbuch, 1937, P. 92, And 1938, P. 98). Source: Data For 1911-1919: Vierteljahrshefte Statistik, 1926, Vol. I, P. 51. Data For 1920-1937: Statistiches Jahrbuch

This NBER data series a01032b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
